            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "5dfe31c513ea4a71ab090",
                    "stepText": "Let's start by recalling the relation for the decay constant. Identify the correct formula that relates the decay constant $!$\\lambda$!$ to the half-life $!$T_{1/2}$!$.",
